16
00:00:38,991 --> 00:00:40,174


17
00:00:40,267 --> 00:00:40,973
buông ra...

18
00:00:41,345 --> 00:00:42,623
Tối nay chúng ta sẽ thoát.

19
00:00:42,716 --> 00:00:45,187
Michael, có chuyện lớn rồi.

20
00:00:45,279 --> 00:00:46,844
không ! không ! 

21
